### Indexing fasta file
$BT2_HOME/bowtie2-build fasta.fa index_name

### Run mapping for SE data to generate unsorted sam file

$BT2_HOME/bowtie2 -x index_name -U reads_1.fq -S example1.sam

### Run mapping for PE data to generate unsorted sam file

$BT2_HOME/bowtie2 -x index_name -1 reads_1.fq -2 reads_2.fq -S example2.sam



